<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="patient-adj">patient <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'peɪʃnt/    美 /'peɪʃnt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>有耐心的；容忍的：</strong></h4>
<p>反 impatient  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>was</strong> usually <strong>patient with</strong> her students and never made them disappointed. 
她对学生通常很有耐心，从来不让他们失望。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>patiently /'peɪʃntli/ adv   </p></div>